{"title":"Tomcat内存溢出问腿解决","date":"2019-04-28T00:42:22.000Z","link":"post/330","categories":["tomcat"],"updated":"2019-04-29T14:38:39.959Z","content":"<p><img src=\"http://pqiuhq1tw.bkt.clouddn.com/20190428170936.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n<p>###解决方法1<br><figure class=\"highlight xml\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">打开catalina.sh文件，添加</span><br><span class=\"line\">JAVA_OPTS=\"-server -Xms1024m -Xmx1024m -XX:PermSize=512M -XX:MaxPermSize=1024m\"</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>###解决方法2<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">可能是因为tomcat进程没有完全关闭，需要手动关闭</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//查看tomcat进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">ps aux | grep tomcat</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//根据PID关闭tomcat进程</span><br><span class=\"line\">kill -9</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n","prev":{"title":"Docker File","link":"post/334"},"next":{"title":"Docker容器","link":"post/333"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/330/"}